# OSS-only paths (electron/, src/oss/) are tracked here in this OSS folder.
# They must NEVER sync back into the main repo's src/ tree.
# That direction is enforced by ../scripts/oss-only.txt + the sync script;
# .gitignore here exists only to keep build/runtime junk out of git.
